Title: Chicken Hill
Writer: Joe Gayton (creator), Tony Gayton (creator), John Wirth, Tom Brady (story)
Actors: Anson Mount, Colm Meaney, Jennifer Ferrin, Robin McLeavy
Plot: Cullen returns to Cheyenne. After being considered dead his return is a shock for many. Bohannan meets a few old friends and makes new enemies whilst trying to get his old job back from Durant.
